main event: A UFO was observed in Munday, New York on 17 May 1955, described as round and green and white in color.
interesting points: The UFO was observed to be motionless for approximately 5 minutes., The object exhibited irregular movement patterns., Witness reported the UFO appeared to have wings but its construction was unclear., Clear weather conditions with excellent visibility at the time of the sighting., Two sightings were reported in Munday, New York in May 1955.
sighted object: one round green and white object
